Package: TreeLS
Type: Package
Title: Tools for terrestrial point cloud processing of forest data
Version: 1.2
Authors@R: c(person("Tiago", "de Conto", email = "ti@forlidar.com.br", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Algorithms for tree detection, point cloud denoising, stem modelling, 3D visualization of terrestrial LiDAR (but not only) point clouds, currently focusing on dendrometry and forest inventory high performance applications - thanks to 'Rcpp', 'rlas' and 'lidR' integrations.
URL: https://github.com/tiagodc/TreeLS    
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), Rcpp (>= 1.0.0), lidR (>= 2.0.0), magrittr (>= 1.5)
Imports: rgl
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp,BH,RcppEigen
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
